Package com.motivewave.platform.sdk.common.desc

Class SettingDescriptor

java.lang.Object
com.motivewave.platform.sdk.common.desc.SettingDescriptor
Direct Known Subclasses:
BarDescriptor, BarSizeDescriptor, BooleanDescriptor, ColorDescriptor, DateTimeDescriptor, DiscreteDescriptor, DoubleDescriptor, ExitPointDescriptor, FileDescriptor, FontDescriptor, GuideDescriptor, IndicatorDescriptor, InputDescriptor, InstrumentDescriptor, IntegerDescriptor, LabelDescriptor, MAMethodDescriptor, MarkerDescriptor, OrderTypeDescriptor, PathDescriptor, PercentSliderDescriptor, PriceBarDescriptor, ShadeDescriptor, SliderDescriptor, SpacerDescriptor, StringDescriptor, TifDescriptor, TimeFrameDescriptor
public abstract class SettingDescriptor extends Object
Base class for all setting descriptors. Instances of this class are used to describe settings that may be configured at runtime by the user.
